Userguide:
step 1: When put the code in a new computer(Linux system),get into the dictionary:
        [username pwd] chmod 744 compil clean
step 2: Change the parameter in "param" and "hop", the detail of the parameter is 
        write in "edhubbard.f90". 
        [username pwd] vi edhubbard.f90
		[username pwd] vi param
        [username pwd] vi hop
step 3: Compile the code
        [username pwd] ./compil
step 4: run the program
        [username pwd] nohup ./lanh &
step 5: see the process in nohup.out
        [username pwd] vi nohup.out
step 6: when the program is over, read the result in eigenvalue.dat and eigenstatei.dat
step 7: get your data out, remove the useless information: lanh,*.dat,*.mod,*.out
        [username pwd] ./clean

 

update:
       Just use Makefile to compile the code and run the code.
         
